      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CORLESS SNEAKY (1) missed the frame on debut then used the inside draw to advantage and broke through for her maiden success last time, scoring by 1.75 lengths at Nowra over 365m (21.19). Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Further improved and looks the one to beat again. ALL ON KYLIE (2) proved too good last time out claiming her maiden success at this track over 320m (18.56). Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. DESTINY OUR GIRL (4) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 0.8 lengths win at Wagga in a handy 18.43. Jumping from the pinch draw but likes the trip. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. In top form and looks a key chance again. NO SHAME (8) is a last-start placegetter from this box – sure to have admirers.",
